WEBVTT

35:12.524 --> 35:14.983
I needed some money for
my daughter's higher education.

35:15.358 --> 35:16.899
Well, what are you doing here?

35:17.524 --> 35:19.274
I'm here to see the DGP.

35:19.691 --> 35:21.316
Actor Harikumar is coming as well.

35:21.858 --> 35:24.274
A pirated version of our film
has leaked.
